<br />\n<br />\n(申：AL Phy A01)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T11:45:44.000Z","msg":"CW Sham 真心勁 <br />\n樓主要快d開竅先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n其實要多做清concept 既練習，一定做有solution 果d, 做完不論對錯都要睇晒個solution / 解釋。 錯左既要mark低錯既地方同重點，每一個星期就睇返之前做過既練習（特別係錯既部分） <br />\n<br />\n日子有功，好快見效。"},{"pid":"2289c25e7802fc8c96347aad06e02cce871852f5","tid":1007971,"uid":109629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T11:58:35.000Z","msg":"認真CW Sham啲notes好正<br />\n以前成班同學仔會share notes<br />\n務求集齊晒成套cw sham全syllabus notes<br />\n<br />\n我以前中四果陣成績普普通通，最尾都係做paper做得多到某個point就會突然間明左個concept<br />\n建議唔好死背/死讀書<br />\nPhysics係要做的，你唔明 唔識唔緊要，俾多少少時間 操操下卷就會明<br />\n<br />\n由淺入深 做下以前CE卷 再做難少少既AL卷都有幫助<br />\n<br />\n同埋最好搵到良師益友互相交流 教學相長就更加事半功倍<br />\n<br />\n樓主俾心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸2013DSE Phy 5*"},{"pid":"1d7850fe01e2507f843b953f0382b6a266d25336","tid":1007971,"uid":62841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661abb0070941355ee5e2bf3cf9e3066bdf2b57b","tid":1007971,"uid":200445,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5abf4dff72f48ec8d614a45340124d51d2e697f5","tid":1007971,"uid":225868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T06:50:03.000Z","msg":"借account <br />\n而家F5, 有讀M2,上堂好似明晒，但每次做題目考試都抄哂，之前補過Wayne Leung，都冇用，真心想問曾經考過Phy的巴絲打點樣可以清concept，又或者有冇好補習老師介紹🙏🙏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:47:46.000Z","msg":"補Wayne leung梗係收皮啦，2018dse都錯幾條，phy一定補cwsham"},{"pid":"ae186a21747b49cd722c0491df06b7f293fdfe08","tid":1007971,"uid":129030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"966f3036c3da965355073a8ba74b61a09c015b56","tid":1007971,"uid":149178,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T07:00:03.000Z","msg":"做past paper錯邊條咪睇返有step答案睇下自己錯邊度唔明邊度囉 <br />\n<br />\n不嬲讀書都冇捷徑 唔明更加要做多啲 但唔好死做爛做唔諗 最重要係做嗰陣慢慢領悟個concept"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:51:49.000Z","msg":"做完用excel mark 返低錯乜，點解錯，可以好似咁分<br />\n綠：全對<br />\n黃：做到，但花左好耐，錯步驟<br />\n紅：完全唔識<br />\n<br />\n將黃、紅既隔一段時間再做<br />\n連做兩次都得就叫過關<br />\n<br />\n慢慢就有進步架啦"},{"pid":"ec344c29cbd4f9200abba8139c8de347acb40823","tid":1007971,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:57:52.000Z","msg":"唔明relativity點算,spacetime 好難明  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f922157c31da781d49e665bd2905d3e42e432b21","tid":1007971,"uid":225868,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T13:16:14.000Z","msg":"多謝各位高人指點，你哋個個都好好人，係年三十晚都有咁多人賜教，感激!!!小弟返去努力用你哋的方法去認真讀!!"},{"pid":"d9021428754bf5b9c3d82d43b007f69a7a1aecd7","tid":1007971,"uid":119145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"認真答你 天份<br />\nPhy好講天份"},{"pid":"383a4d3d73489fa82874376708f2b5211fbde325","tid":1007971,"uid":171256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T15:48:57.000Z","msg":"數學對DSE物理嘅幫助:<br />\n圖形嘅處理: slope/area可以用calculus去諗<br />\nVector：mechanics，EM有好多vector嘅數，包括scalar product/ vector product<br />\nVariation: 熟左，好多DSE ratio問題可以秒<br />\n<br />\n你想拿高啲分<br />\n建議<br />\nSolar MC + Pearson 兩本<br />\n(Textbook Ex/Radian依家都幾離地)<br />\n學嗰陣學深少少，大學textbook可以做參考"},{"pid":"ecd77b81a82283ce5c9cb526648214b998ca8d3f","tid":1007971,"uid":68753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T19:19:01.000Z","msg":"唔同人有唔同諗野嘅方法<br />\n最好諗清楚你自己嘅困難係邊<br />\n比如係理解文字有困難<br />\n定係理解公式有困難<br />\n定係運算有困難<br />\n<br />\n中學程度數底好嘅話物理應該無難度<br />\n真係要諗清楚點解你會做到數<br />\n但物理d concept會get唔到<br />\n而且中學物理其實極少內容<br />\n來來去去都係果d, 要清應該好快清晒"},{"pid":"6301f5552ae1213681c63db399e70d42a084603c","tid":1007971,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec344c29cbd4f9200abba8139c8de347acb40823","tid":1007971,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:57:52.000Z","msg":"唔明relativity點算,spacetime 好難明  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T19:36:29.000Z","msg":"我mechanics已經搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}